\">8.</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">先打开</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\"> Winscp.exe</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family:宋体\">程序；</span></p><p><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_0ktwkzwdfcgbows.png\" width=\"605\" height=\"162\"/></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">9.</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">直接点击登录</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">如果你后台密码修改了的话点击</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">root</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">下的编辑来修改密码，<strong><span style=\"color:fuchsia\">如果提示任何错误直接按确定即可</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;color:fuchsia\">!</span></strong></p><p><span>&nbsp;<img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_51i83r6syms2cjm.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"430\"/></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">10. </span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">点击右侧的</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">...</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">，找到</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">tmp</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">文件夹双击进入；</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_dsi4cdqjb9gfcqb.jpg\" width=\"1090\" height=\"700\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_2xvj5tec8ymceve.jpg\" width=\"1090\" height=\"700\"/></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">11. <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从官方下载固件：https://app.hiwifi.com/dstore.php?m=download&amp;a=info</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family:宋体\">重命名固件名字为</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">123.bin</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">