</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"476\" height=\"352\" src=\"file:///C:/Users/zycsn/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image038.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span><img border=\"0\" width=\"666\" height=\"413\" src=\"file:///C:/Users/zycsn/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image039.jpg\"/></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">123.bin</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">就是极路由的固件</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">注意</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">-F</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">要大写</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\"> !!</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 29px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: 宋体;color:fuchsia\">路由器开始刷机，此时路由器指示灯会跑马灯似的依次闪烁！</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 29px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 29px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 29px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: 宋体;color:fuchsia\">等待</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">分钟，千万不能断电，然后尝试进入</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">http://192.168.199.1</span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">如果无法进入，尝试复位：上电情况下，用牙签捅住后面板</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:fuchsia\">RST</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">孔</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:fuchsia\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: 宋体;color:fuchsia\">秒，松开，等待重启。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p>'  WHERE `pid`='28' 
