isc;\">-q 较少的输出信息</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;\">-v 详细的输出信息</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;\">-h 显示帮助信息</li></ul><h3 id=\"备份选项\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">备份选项：</h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;\">-b | --create-backup&nbsp;<file style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>把sysupgrade.conf 里描述的文件打包成.tar.gz 作为备份，不做烧写动作</file></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;\">-r | --restore-backup&nbsp;<file style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>从-b 命令创建的 .tar.gz 文件里恢复配置，不做烧写动作</file></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;\">-l | --list-backup<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>列出 -b 命令将备份的文件列表，但不创建备份文件</li></ul><p style=\"line-height: 29px\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 29px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: 宋体;color:fuchsia\">等待</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">分钟，千万不能断电，然后尝试进入</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:fuchsia\">http://192.168.199.1</span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">如果无法进入，尝试复位：上电情况下，用牙签捅住后面板</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:fuchsia\">RST</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">孔</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:fuchsia