eight=\"430\"/></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">10. </span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">点击右侧的</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">...</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">，找到</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">tmp</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">文件夹双击进入；</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_dsi4cdqjb9gfcqb.jpg\" width=\"1090\" height=\"700\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_2xvj5tec8ymceve.jpg\" width=\"1090\" height=\"700\"/></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">11. <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从官方下载固件：https://app.hiwifi.com/dstore.php?m=download&amp;a=info</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family:宋体\">重命名固件名字为</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">123.bin</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\"><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_gdfdh46ydz7cd6k.jpg\" width=\"1089\" height=\"703\"/></span></p><p></p><p><span><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_9u2k6u2vxfca5t0.jpg\" width=\"1052\" height=\"700\"/></span></p><p><span><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_u42ayfi6hao4mnk.jpg\" width=\"1052\" height=\"700\"/></span></p><p><span><img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_b7h7kr9wd2p911e.jpg\" width=\"1052\" height=\"700\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">、打开文件夹中的</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">Putty.exe </span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family:宋体\">程序；</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;<img src=\"http://blog.zycsnd.cn/upload/attach/201703/1_5ie66lkhq4pu981.png\" width=\"456\" height=\"403\"/></span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\">要确定您的